name: Sessions
body:
### Welcome to UWC Algorithm Circle(beta).
This algorithm circles serves as a space for students to sharpen their problem solving and analytical skills. We hope that you find this society helpful to you and your future endeavours:


### Misc
While we, _the knights of the round table_, will provide interesting problems to test your analytical skills we hope that you will approach the circle with your own set of problems that you find interesting. One of the most important ideas we have in mind is that you shall someday, too, become a _knight of the round table_ and lead our forces to victory (^_^)v. 


### Authors and Contributors
_UWC knights of the round table_



```
I am not a man of codes.
But I respect the power of codes, for that is what transformed me.
The codes of the Turing.
Others had heard them, contemplated them, and so on.
But I understood them, and they changed me.
For what was I before I understood those codes?
Nothing.
```
